{
  "texts": [
    "As discussed in the literature, components of the rhetorical situation may compliment prompts or input texts through their similar methods.",
    "For our experiments, we chose the GPT-3 model for its exceptional advancement and relevancy.",
    "In this section we describe the instruments, procedure, and analysis method integral to our research.",
    "Under a mixed-methods (qualitative and quantitative feedback based) approach, we developed prompt variations prior to the experiment, in a word processing document, and labeled their components of the rhetorical situation (see Appendix for variations).",
    "Three genres, user guide, proposal, white paper and memo, were selected for the experiment owing to (1) their relevance to the technical writing field and (2) distinct characteristics that will allow seamless comparisons."
  ]
}